videos.description: Matt Farrell dishes the ball to Matt Ryan who drains the 3-pointer over the defender for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Farrell finds Ryan for the 3-pointer

videos.description: Mike Brey talks about his team play and how they are defending Dennis Smith Jr.
videos.headline: Mike Brey talks about his team's first half shooting

videos.description: Matt Farrell goes towards the baseline while drawing two defenders and gives the nice bounce pass to Austin Torres who finishes with the jam.
videos.headline: Farrell draws two defenders and dishes to Torres for the dunk

videos.description: Bonzie Colson gets the contact and drains the jumper plus the foul.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Colson muscles his way for the and-1 jumper
